data.description: Charming Traditional on the best street in Woodbridge! This stunning 2-story home has stunning curb appeal, energy-certified windows, and stainless steel appliances. It welcomes you with fresh paint and beautiful new waterproof and scratch-resistant laminate flooring on the first floor. No carpet on the first floor. The layout offers a formal study upon entry, with an adjacent elegant formal dining room. An island kitchen w/ 42" cabinets, butler's pantry w/ added wine chiller! Oversized family room area and primary bedroom on the first floor that offers its owners a relaxing retreat with a luxurious bath and 2 walk-in closets! The second floor offers an enormous raised floor game room, surround sound and media room! 2 Full baths all w/ new toilets and 3 additional bedrooms! A peaceful, oversized, covered back porch tops this beauty off perfect for you backyard "shindig"! Convenient location within minutes access to 59 and Kingwood! Home has never flooded! Schedule your showings today!
